  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1900970/extras/1b407f879ca18b815e33270dda63057c.avif?t=1696715799\" width=600 height=117 /></span><br><strong>The Red Hood</strong> is a horror game, based on \"Little Red riding hood\" folks.<br><br>The Red Hood is a first-person horror-memory game, where the main character is lost in the woods and you are not alone, there is a serial killer with a wolf mask and your main goal is to avoid him. <br>The gameplay is simple you should choose the right path to avoid a serial killer with a wolf mask if you die you will start the game from the beginning, remember the right paths, and good luck.<br><br>Features:<br>*Atmospheric visual<br>*Unique Mechanic<br>*Emotional gameplay<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1900970/extras/01987034ccabf542eddca2bfc68bf866.avif?t=1696715799\" width=620 height=338 /></span>",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1900970/extras/1b407f879ca18b815e33270dda63057c.avif?t=1696715799\" width=600 height=117 /></span><br><strong>The Red Hood</strong> is a horror game, based on \"Little Red riding hood\" folks.<br><br>The Red Hood is a first-person horror-memory game, where the main character is lost in the woods and you are not alone, there is a serial killer with a wolf mask and your main goal is to avoid him. <br>The gameplay is simple you should choose the right path to avoid a serial killer with a wolf mask if you die you will start the game from the beginning, remember the right paths, and good luck.<br><br>Features:<br>*Atmospheric visual<br>*Unique Mechanic<br>*Emotional gameplay<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1900970/extras/01987034ccabf542eddca2bfc68bf866.avif?t=1696715799\" width=620 height=338 /></span>",
